name: Ogbunabali
shortLoreBlurb: Ogbunabali is a deity/spirit from Igbo associated with death at night, justice. Mediates funerary order and soul journeys.
overlapsLinks: Anubis (Egyptian), Athena (Greek), Chandra (Hindu), Chang'e (China), Hades (Greek), Hel (Norse), Karttikeya (Hindu), Mama Quilla (Inca), Morrigan (Celtic), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Tsukuyomi (Japan), Yama (Buddhist)
